<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='607780' id='t-607780'>And one idea comes from lessons from chewing crabs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='610855' id='t-610855'>And I don't mean chewing the crabs.</span>
