<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621208' id='t-621208'>Crabs have this complicated structure under their carapace</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='624467' id='t-624467'>called the gastric mill</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625777' id='t-625777'>that grinds their food in a variety of different ways.</span>
