<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698525' id='t-698525'>Is there any evidence that flies do this?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700619' id='t-700619'>Well, for many years in my laboratory and other laboratories around the world,</span>
